{"id":14203,"date":"2025-11-04T09:21:19","date_gmt":"2025-11-04T14:21:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=14203"},"modified":"2025-11-04T09:21:19","modified_gmt":"2025-11-04T14:21:19","slug":"journee-mondiale-de-la-gentillesse","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/journee-mondiale-de-la-gentillesse\/","title":{"rendered":"Journ\u00e9e mondiale de la gentillesse"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Pour l\u2019occasion de la Journ\u00e9e mondiale de la gentillesse, le 13 novembre prochain, la Direction des services aux \u00e9tudiants et la Direction des ressources humaines font \u00e9quipe pour offrir deux activit\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019ensemble de notre communaut\u00e9 afin de souligner la sant\u00e9 mentale au coll\u00e9gial.<\/p>\n<p>Viens tourner la roue de la gentillesse, en \u00e9change d\u2019une collation. Tu recevras un d\u00e9fi \u00e0 r\u00e9aliser dans la journ\u00e9e. C\u2019est prouv\u00e9, un simple geste de gentillesse peut changer la journ\u00e9e de quelqu\u2019un.<\/p>\n<p>L\u2019\u00e9quipe de <a href=\"https:\/\/mouvementsmq.ca\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mouvement Sant\u00e9 mentale Qu\u00e9bec<\/a> sera aussi pr\u00e9sente pour discuter sant\u00e9 mentale et bien-\u00eatre. Une occasion simple de te transmettre des pistes de r\u00e9flexion, des outils et des ressources dont les sept astuces pour se recharger.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":14204,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2357],"class_list":["post-14203","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:37:07","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"categorieevenement"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement\/14203","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/evenement"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14204"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14203"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorieevenement","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorieevenement?post=14203"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=14203"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}